headline: GTA Online
subtitle: BF Weevil Custom (Benny's)
content: Ah, post-drive clarity. When you’ve gone from 0-100 in the spur of the moment, and now that it’s over you’re left wondering whether you’re mentally sound. Full disclosure: Driving the BF Weevil Custom is a kink, but when you take the key out of the ignition, there’s only one immediate realization. True love. Eligible for customization at Benny’s Original Motor Works.
